---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

// Replace these placeholders before launch
const calendarUrl = 'https://cal.com/your-handle/30min'; // Cal.com or Calendly URL
const emailAddress = 'hello@thinkingmachine.eu';        // Or whatever you decide
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Contact — Thinking Machine"
  description="Thirty minutes, no slides, no pitch. Book a free intro to discuss a fixed-scope advisory engagement."
>
  <article class="container-page py-20 md:py-28">
    <header class="max-w-prose mb-12">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-ink-900 leading-tight">Contact</h1>
      <p class="mt-6 text-xl text-ink-700 leading-relaxed">
        Thirty minutes, no slides, no pitch.
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="prose max-w-prose">
      <p>
        The first call is always free. We use it to understand the problem and decide together
        whether we can help. If we do not think Thinking Machine is the right fit, we will say
        so on the call and, where possible, point you to someone better suited.
      </p>

      <h2>Book a call</h2>
      <p>
        <a href={calendarUrl} class="btn-primary not-prose">
          Book a 30-minute intro →
        </a>
      </p>

      <p>
        If the calendar is not loading or you would rather email first, write to
        <strong><a href={`mailto:${emailAddress}`}>{emailAddress}</a></strong>
        and we will get back to you within one working day.
      </p>

      <h2>What to send ahead</h2>
      <p>
        A few sentences on the problem. The deadline if there is one. Any documents that frame
        the question. We will read what you send before the call.
      </p>
      <p>
        We treat all pre-engagement communications as confidential. We do not maintain a CRM.
        We do not subscribe you to a newsletter. We do not share your inquiry with anyone outside
        Thinking Machine.
      </p>

      <h2>Where we work</h2>
      <p>
        Zagreb, Croatia, with engagements across the European Union. Remote-first. We travel for
        kickoff and final-readout meetings when the engagement warrants it.
      </p>

      <h2>What we charge</h2>
      <p>
        Engagement fees depend on shape and scope; we will quote a fixed fee on the first call before
        any commitment. We do not bill hourly. There are no expansion clauses. We do not charge for
        the introductory thirty minutes regardless of outcome.
      </p>
    </section>

    <hr class="section-divider mx-auto max-w-prose" />

    <footer class="max-w-prose text-sm text-ink-500">
      <p><strong class="text-ink-800">Thinking Machine d.o.o.</strong></p>
      <p>Zagreb, Croatia · Founded 2022</p>
      <p>OIB: <span class="text-ink-700">[OIB number]</span></p>
      <p>Registered office: <span class="text-ink-700">[Registered address]</span></p>
    </footer>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
